Sinister got bored of destroying Quickstrike and Sinesis and decided that
they wouldn't go anywhere and he needed to get that otter......he walked off
in the direction of Kit while Sinesis struggled to get to his
feet.....Sinister found here.....he pulled his gun, set it to mass
explosion, and shot it, that way, he blew up the whole area..unfortunentley,
it also meant blowing himseld up, but nah!.....just to give that otter a
little damage it would be worth it.....he fired....the area within 50 feet
exploded under the bomb he launched......

> =======

the back of his neck and shooting down point-blank at his neck!*
